                     <interp inst="t18390408-1344-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18390408-cd-178" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390408-1344-offence-1 t18390408-cd-178"></join>2nd of April</rs>, 10 pence, and 15 halfpence, the monies of <persName id="t18390408-name-1091" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-1091" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
